snippet.title: Diana Barbie and Roma Ken Pink vs. Blue Challenge
snippet.description:
Diana loves the pink color and the Barbie style. Roma likes blue and dresses like Ken. They are different, opposite! But they must help each other to cope with the problems that arise. New Pink vs Blue Challenge with Diana and Roma.
